---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="AJ Gamble | Strategic Operations & Sales"
	description="Driving operational excellence and revenue growth."
	heroImage="/strategic-bg.jpg"
>
	<div class="hero-section" style="padding: 4rem 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #000;">
		<h1 style="font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
			Transforming Operational Friction into Scalable Success.
		</h1>
		<p style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #444; max-width: 800px;">
			I bridge the gap between technical operations and revenue growth. From international supply chain logistics to high-performance inside sales leadership, I build systems that last.
		</p>
		<div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
			<a href="/about" style="background: #000; color: #fff; padding: 1rem 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 4px;">
				View My Operational Philosophy
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <h2>The Strategic Edge</h2>
        <p>I don't believe in "band-aid" fixes. I believe in architectural solutions that eliminate bottlenecks, optimize throughput, and maximize customer value.</p>
    </div>
</Layout>